    "en": {
      "name": "Dragon Tail Gramel",
      "effect": "1 \"Dragon Tail\" monster + 1 monster in the hand\nWhen you activate a \"Dragon Tail\" card or effect (Quick Effect): You can target 1 card your opponent controls; destroy it. If 2 or more monsters are sent to the GY at the same time while this card is in your GY (except during the Damage Step): You can Special Summon this card, but banish it when it leaves the field. You can only use each effect of \"Dragon Tail Gramel\" once per turn.",
      "official": false
    },
